Package: rmstnma
Title: Restricted Mean Survival Time Network Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mahmood", "Ahmad", , "mahmood726@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9107-3704"))
Description: Implements Bayesian network meta-analysis for restricted mean 
    survival time (RMST) outcomes. Provides functions for data preparation,
    model fitting using Stan, diagnostic tools for restriction time selection, 
    and result visualization. Handles Kaplan-Meier reconstruction uncertainty 
    and exports results in formats suitable for evidence synthesis.
